'''杨新社'''（{{lang-en|Xin-She Yang}}；{{bd|1965年|catIdx=Yang Xin-She}}），原籍[[河南省|河南省]][[尉氏县|尉氏县]]，[[華裔英國人|華裔英國]][[计算机科学|计算机科学]]家，[[英国国家物理实验室|英国国家物理实验室]]高级研究科学家。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://math.xpu.edu.cn/info/1364/2787.htm|title=杨新社|website=西安工程大學理學院|date=2012-12-08|accessdate=2021-08-07|archive-date=2021-08-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210807142612/https://math.xpu.edu.cn/info/1364/2787.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>牛津大学應用数学[[哲學博士|哲学博士]]<ref>[http://www.ox.ac.uk/gazette/1997-8/weekly/050298/exam.htm Oxford University Gazette] {{Wayback|url=http://www.ox.ac.uk/gazette/1997-8/weekly/050298/exam.htm|date=20120928071146}}</ref>。目前任教於[[密德薩斯大學|密德薩斯大學]]。

== 學術貢獻 ==
楊新社在[[剑桥大学|剑桥大学]]创新和发展了3種[[啟發式演算法|启发式优化算法]]包括：[[萤火虫算法|萤火虫算法]]<ref name="firefly2008" />（2008年）、[[布谷鸟搜索算法|布谷鸟搜索算法]]<ref name="cuckoo2009" /><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2010/05/100527213816.htm |title=Novel 'cuckoo search algorithm' beats particle swarm optimization in engineering design |publisher=Sciencedaily.com |date=2010-05-28 |accessdate=2013-05-14 |archive-date=2020-11-09 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201109032223/http://www.sciencedaily.com/releases/2010/05/100527213816.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite web |author=Tue, 06/01/2010 - 12:07pm |url=http://www.scientificcomputing.com/news-DA-Novel-Cuckoo-Search-Algorithm-Beats-Particle-Swarm-Optimization-060110.aspx |title=Novel 'Cuckoo Search Algorithm' Beats Particle Swarm Optimization |publisher=Scientificcomputing.com |date= |accessdate=2013-05-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120311231333/http://www.scientificcomputing.com/news-DA-Novel-Cuckoo-Search-Algorithm-Beats-Particle-Swarm-Optimization-060110.aspx |archive-date=2012-03-11 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>（2009）和[[蝙蝠算法|蝙蝠算法]]<ref>Yang X.-S., A New Metaheuristic Bat-Inspired Algorithm, in: Nature Inspired Cooperative Strategies for Optimization (NISCO 2010) (Eds. J. R. Gonzalez et al.), Studies in Computational Intelligence, Springer Berlin, 284, Springer, 65–74 (2010)</ref>（2010），另發表許多仿生算法相關論文。

多次应邀为至国际学术大会做主题演讲，如SEA2011<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.rebennack.net/SEA2011/ |title=SEA 2011 - 10th International Symposium on Experimental Algorithms |publisher=Rebennack.net |date= |accessdate=2013-05-14 |archive-date=2017-03-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170330043132/http://www.rebennack.net/SEA2011/ |dead-url=no }}</ref> ，BIOMA2012 <ref>{{cite web |url=http://bioma.ijs.si/conference/2012/ |title=BIOMA 2012 |publisher=Bioma.ijs.si |date= |accessdate=2013-05-14 |archive-date=2013-02-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130227173913/http://bioma.ijs.si/conference/2012/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，孟德尔软计算大会（Mendel'2012），国际计算科学会议（ICCS2015）及巴西国际计算机科学及图像处理年会（SIBGRAP2015)。

其發明的算法已成为重要的优化工具，在[[人工智能|人工智能]]<ref>Yang X. S., Artificial Intelligence, Evolutionary Computing and Metaheuristics, Springer, (2013)</ref>，[[机器学习|机器学习]]，[[数据挖掘|数据挖掘]]，神经计算，[[优化|优化设计]]及工程等有重要的应用<ref>Yang X. S. et al., Metaheuristics in Water, Geotechnical and Transport Engineering, Esleveir, (2012).</ref><ref> Yang X. S. and Koziel S., Computational Optimization and Applications in Engineering and Industry, Springer, (2011). </ref>。2009年以来，约有2200多篇关于萤火虫算法、布谷鸟搜索、蝙蝠算法的[[学术期刊|学术期刊]]研究论文。

與van Flander共同提出[[Flandern-Yang假设|Flandern-Yang假设]]<ref>{{cite journal|title=What's the matter with gravity?|date=18 August 2000|doi=10.1038/news000824-1}} http://www.nature.com/news/2000/000818/full/news000824-1.html {{Wayback|url=http://www.nature.com/news/2000/000818/full/news000824-1.html |date=20161206065238 }}</ref><ref>Yang X. S. and Wang Q. S., Gravity anomaly during the Mohe total solar eclipse and new constraint on gravitational shielding parameter, Astrophysics and Space Science, Vol. 282, 245–253 (2002).</ref> ，这一理论是与著名的[[阿莱效应|阿莱效应]]（Allais effect)来解释重力变化等现象有关<ref>Duif C. P.,http://arxiv.org/ftp/gr-qc/papers/0408/0408023.pdf {{Wayback|url=http://arxiv.org/ftp/gr-qc/papers/0408/0408023.pdf |date=20210829074922 }}</ref><ref>G. Schilling, New Scientist,  Vol. 184, No. 2475, Page 28, "Shadow over gravity" (27 Nov 2004)http://homepage.mac.com/turder/iblog/B561081935/C1798329063/E2125615711/index.html{{dead link|date=2018年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>，曾經在[[印尼|印尼]]的国家日报报导<ref>（KOMPAS）http://print.kompas.com/baca/2016/02/24/Gravitasi-Bumi-Terpengaruh-tetapi-Tak-Signifikan {{Wayback|url=http://print.kompas.com/baca/2016/02/24/Gravitasi-Bumi-Terpengaruh-tetapi-Tak-Signifikan |date=20160827092910 }}</ref>。

